	  {
		"id": "t_herb_gathering",
		"name": "Forage in Sun-Dappled Meadows",
		"desc": "Join your brothers in the meadows beyond the village wall, baskets in hand, to collect sun-herb, marrowroot, and silverleaf.",
		"extdesc": "Laughter and competition fill the air as you search. Kael finds the biggest patches, while Bren teaches you which leaves are best for poultices. Shadow digs for roots.",
